START

INPUT:
    text
    chunk_size
    overlap

CREATE an empty list called chunks

SET start position = 0
SET chunk ID = 0

WHILE the start position is less than the length of the text:

    Calculate the end position:
        end = smaller of
              (start position + chunk size)
              OR
              (length of text)

    Extract a portion of the text
    from start position up to end position

    Create a chunk record containing:
        - unique chunk ID
        - extracted text
        - starting position
        - ending position
        - length of the extracted text

    Add the chunk record to the chunks list

    Move the start position forward
    BUT keep the specified overlap from the previous chunk

    Increase the chunk ID by 1

    IF the new start position has reached or passed
    the end of the text:
        STOP the loop

RETURN the chunks list

END
